a 9), describes Masutomi Onsen. '''Tanaka Fuyuji''' ({{ill|1894|ja|1894th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1894|qq=}} – {{ill|1980|ja|1980th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1980|qq=}}) was a banker who also wrote poetry and essays. In Yamanashi Prefecture, besides Masutomi Onsen, he visited {{ill|Narata Onsen|ja|奈良田温泉|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Narata Onsen|qq=}} (in Minami-Koma District, Hayakawa Town). In 1955 (Showa 30), he visited Masutomi Onsen with his family and the painter {{ill|Tomita Michio|ja|富田通雄|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomita Michio|qq=}}. His essays on Masutomi Onsen include descriptions titled “Mountain Gorge Hot Spring” and “Masutomi Radium Onsen.”
